    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="雅思口语"><a href="#雅思口语" class="headerlink" title="雅思口语"></a>雅思口语</h1><h2 id="Hometown"><a href="#Hometown" class="headerlink" title="Hometown"></a>Hometown</h2><ol><li><p><strong>Where is your hometown?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我的家乡在郑州旁边的乡村里，名字是新密。</span><br><span class="line">My hometown is in the countryside next to Zhengzhou, and it name is Xinmi.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Is it a big city or a small place?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">目前只是一个小农村，很多地方还没有开发。不过当地政府最近两年在进行改造，发展景点和旅游业，以后就会变大了</span><br><span class="line">At present, it is only a small rural area, and many places have not been developed. However, the local government has been renovating in the past two years to develop attractions and tourism, and it will become bigger in the future</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you like your hometown?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">当然，我的家乡环境优美，大大小小的山峰三百多座，植被茂密，有很多的土地资源，矿物资源和植物资源。同时也有悠久的历史文化，也曾是中国的神话人物伏羲女娲的故乡。</span><br><span class="line">Of course, my hometown has a beautiful environment, with more than 300 large and small peaks, dense vegetation, and a lot of land, mineral and plant resources. At the same time, it also has a long history and culture, and was once the hometown of the Chinese mythical figure Fuxi Nuwa.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What do you like most about your hometown?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我最喜欢家乡的环境和慢节奏很小的压力，就像我刚刚说的有很多山，水，植被，环境优美。心情可以得到很好的放松。不像大城市里非常快的节奏，导致心很累。</span><br><span class="line">I lik my hometown environment and slow pace little pressure, like I just said, there are a lot of mountains, water, vegetation, beautiful environment. and the mood can be well relaxed. It&#x27;s not like the very fast pace in big cities, which leads to a very tired heart.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Is there anything you dislike about it?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">有不喜欢的地方，因为是农村，道路小，设施比较老旧，没有强大的公共交通系统。所以生活所需的设备和日常出行都很不方便</span><br><span class="line">There are places not to like, because it is rural, the roads are small, the facilities are relatively old, and there is no strong public transportation system. Therefore, the equipment and daily travel required for life are inconvenient</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>How long have you been living there?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">通常我只在重要的法定节假日回去，因为平常很少有时间只有法定节假日能放假。如果放假时间比较短，如端午节，劳动节只有1天，我可能只会回去十几个小时或者不回去。如果放假时间比较长，如国庆节，春节有3天，我会回去2天。</span><br><span class="line">Usually I only go back on important statutory holidays, because there are usually few times when I can only take holidays on statutory holidays. If the holiday time is relatively short, such as the Dragon Boat Festival, Labor Day is only 1 day, I may only go back for more than ten hours or not go back. If the holiday is longer, such as National Day, there are 3 days for the Spring Festival, I will go back for 2 days.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you like living there?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">是的，我喜欢住在那里。就像我之前说过的，那里环境很好生活的压力也很小。我很享受这样的生活，这可以改变我的心情，不会使我很焦虑。</span><br><span class="line">Yes, I loved staying there. Like I said before, the environment is good and the pressure to live there is very small. I enjoy this kind of life, it can change my mood and it doesn&#x27;t make me anxious.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you think you will continue living there for a long time?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我认为我不会在那里生活很长时间，因为那里没有好工作，而且工资都非常低，我不确定那样能不能养活我。而市中心往往有更好的工作和更多的机会，我需要在城市中去寻找工作。也许在我老了会长时间生活在那里，但目前不会。</span><br><span class="line">I don&#x27;t think I&#x27;m going to live there for long because there are no good jobs and the wages are so low that I&#x27;m not sure if that will feed me. Downtown tends to have better jobs and more opportunities, and I need to look for work in the city. Maybe I&#x27;ll live there for a long time when I&#x27;m old, but not at the moment.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Please describe your hometown a little.</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">好的，新密有悠久的历史、美丽的环境和丰富的资源。它的矿产和粮食价值非常重要，首先是矿物资源主要有煤炭、铝钒土、石灰石、硅石。煤田地质储量50亿吨，其中煤炭工业保有量16.5亿吨，铝钒土储量6000万吨、工业硅储量10亿吨、石灰石储量50亿吨，都极有工业价值。其次是粮食，每年粮食总产量20万吨，主要为小麦、玉米和蔬菜水果。</span><br><span class="line">Well, Xinmi has a long history, beautiful environment and rich resources. Its mineral and food value is very important, first of all, mineral resources mainly include coal, bauxite, limestone, silica. The geological reserves of coalfield are 5 billion tons, of which 1.65 billion tons are in the coal industry, 60 million tons of aluminum-vanadium reserves, 1 billion tons of industrial silicon reserves and 5 billion tons of limestone reserves, all of which have great industrial value. The second is grain, with a total annual grain output of 200,000 tons, mainly wheat, corn, vegetables and fruits.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What’s your hometown famous for?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我的家乡以玉石和烤鱼闻名，首先是玉石。新密是中国著名的密玉产地。在古时即被开发利用。在1960年曾经发现过一块高一点二八米、重一点三五吨的大玉，受到中国领导人称赞。现被列为国宝，保存于上海博物馆。新密玉多用于生产小型玉器和首饰，尤其是绿色密玉生产的饰物或艺术品，深受中外人士喜爱。其次是烤鱼，新密烤鱼能将人们不经常吃甚至讨厌吃的鲇鱼做的很美味，发展到了很多城市。</span><br><span class="line">My hometown is famous for jade and grilled fish, first and foremost jade. Xinmi is a famous source of dense jade in China. It was developed and utilized in ancient times. In 1960, a large piece of jade 1.28 meters high and weighing 1.35 tons was found, which was praised by Chinese leaders. It is now listed as a national treasure and is preserved in the Shanghai Museum. New dense jade is mostly used in the production of small jade and jewelry, especially ornaments or artworks produced by green dense jade, and is deeply loved by Chinese and foreign people. The second is grilled fish, and the new secret grilled fish can make catfish that people don&#x27;t eat often or even hate to eat very delicious, and has developed to many cities.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Did you learn about the history of your hometown at school?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">老实说我在学校并没有学习到家乡的历史，或许只有我家乡的学校才会学习。在中国的历史教育中往往是很有名、有重大事件、有非常大的战略意义的。因为我的家乡只是一个小农村，在中国有很多这样的地方和更有名更好的地方，我的家乡在中国的历史中是很普通甚至是毫不起眼的。所以在学校的历史学习中并没有学到有关我家乡的历史.</span><br><span class="line">To be honest, I didn&#x27;t learn the history of my hometown at school, maybe only my hometown school did. In China&#x27;s history education, it is often very famous, a major event, and of great strategic significance. Because my hometown is just a small rural village, and there are many such places and more famous and better places in China, my hometown is very ordinary and even inconspicuous in China&#x27;s history. So I didn&#x27;t learn about the history of my hometown in the history study at school.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="Home-and-accommodation"><a href="#Home-and-accommodation" class="headerlink" title="Home and accommodation"></a>Home and accommodation</h2><ol><li><p><strong>Do you live in a house or a flat?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我住在公寓在11楼，公寓位置在郑州的南边，离市中心稍微有点远有20多千米。因为那里的价格会便宜一些。</span><br><span class="line">I live on the 11th floor of the apartment, which is located in the south of Zhengzhou, a little bit far from the city center, more than 20 kilometers. Because the price there will be a little cheaper.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Can you describe the place where you live?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我住的地方不大，有90平方米。住着我、父母和妹妹四个人有些紧凑。有三个卧室，两个大的一个小的。两个洗手间，一个厨房，一个客厅和一个阳台。没有单独的餐厅，因为是和客厅连在一起所以只放了一张餐桌。</span><br><span class="line">I live in a small place, 90 square meters. The four people who lived me, my parents and my sister were a bit tight. There are three bedrooms, two large and a small one. Two washrooms, a kitchen, a living room and a balcony. There is no separate dining room, and because it is connected to the living room, there is only one dining table.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>How long have you lived there?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是在高中时搬到了那里，现在有5年了</span><br><span class="line">I moved there in high school and it&#x27;s been 5 years now</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Please describe the room you live in</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我的房间是那个小卧室，所以东西很少。只有一张床，一个连着墙面的衣柜和书桌。床的旁边是一扇窗户，上面有一个小空调。因为房间小，所以即使是小空调也能使房间一直有舒适的温度。</span><br><span class="line">My room was that little bedroom so there were very few things. There is only one bed, a wardrobe and desk attached to the wall. Next to the bed is a window with a small air conditioner on it. Because the room is small, even a small air conditioner can keep the room at a comfortable temperature all the time.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What part of your home do you like the most</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我最喜欢家里的客厅。首先因为它是我家里最大的空间，然后有一张柔软的大沙发躺着很舒服，最后是在家里的中间位置，光线也很好。</span><br><span class="line">I like the living room in my home the most. First because it&#x27;s the biggest space in my home, then there&#x27;s a big soft sofa that&#x27;s comfortable to lie on, and finally it&#x27;s in the middle of the home and it&#x27;s also very light.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Who do you live with?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">家里一共住四个人，我、父母和妹妹。不过我是自己单独住一个房间，我喜欢有自己的私人空间，不会觉得很压抑和心累</span><br><span class="line">There were four people living in the family, me, my parents and my sister. However, I live in a room by myself, and I like to have my own private space, without feeling very depressed and tired</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What room does your family spend most of the time in?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我想餐厅应该是一起时间最多的，因为平时父母要上班，我和妹妹上学。所以家里白天大部分时间没有人。晚上回来也比较晚，大部分时间都在自己的房间睡觉了。所以一般只有早餐时都会在餐厅度过</span><br><span class="line">I think the restaurant should spend the most time together, because usually my parents have to go to work and my sister and I go to school. So there is no one at home most of the day. I came back late in the evening and slept in my room most of the time. Therefore, I usually spend it in the restaurant only at breakfast</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What do you usually do in your flat?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我通常在公寓里吃饭睡觉，因为我要上学，大部分时间在学校。有时放假了会在公寓里玩游戏和看电视。</span><br><span class="line">I usually eat and sleep in the apartment because I have to go to school, most of the time at school. Sometimes when I have a holiday, I play games and watch TV in the apartment.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What kinds of accommodation do you live in?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">因为我住的是公寓，所以每个房间几乎都是矩形。每一层楼有四个邻居。而且地方不大，会有些拥挤</span><br><span class="line">As I stayed in an apartment, each room was almost rectangular. There are four neighbors on each floor. And the place is not big, it will be a little crowded</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you plan to live there for a long time?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我想并不会，因为以后我可能会去别的城市工作和生活，所以不会住很长时间，也许就二年</span><br><span class="line">I think not, because I may go to other cities to work and live in the future, so I will not live for a long time, maybe two years</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you prefer living in a house or a flat?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">如果有钱的话我更喜欢住在房子里，因为房子很大，我几乎不用担心我有很多的东西没地方放，我想放很多有趣的设备。而且，我可以装修成我喜欢的样子。</span><br><span class="line">If I have money, I prefer to live in a house, because the house is big, I hardly have to worry that I have a lot of things that I don&#x27;t have to put and I want to put a lot of interesting equipment. Moreover, I can decorate it to my liking.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Are the transport facilities to you home very good?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">因为我家在市中心的边缘，所以不是很好，中间需要换乘别的车。不过总是能有一个交通线路到达我家</span><br><span class="line">Because my house is on the edge of the city center, it is not very good, and I need to change other cars in the middle. But there is always a transport line to my house</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What kind of house or flat do you want to live in the future?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">如果有钱的话，我未来想住有一个地下室，一个车库和两层或者三层的大房子。地下室主要用来停车和储藏物资，车库主要用来维修车，因为我喜欢车，也喜欢能自己动手做一些简单的修理和改造，就需要在车库有很多的维修工具。</span><br><span class="line">If I have money, I would like to live in a basement, a garage and a large house with two or three floors. The basement is mainly used for parking and storing supplies, and the garage is mainly used to repair the car, because I like the car, and I like to be able to do some simple repairs and modifications by myself, so I need to have a lot of maintenance tools in the garage.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What’s your favorite room in your apartment&#x2F;house?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我想一定是我的游戏间。如果有一个游戏间，我会毫不吝测的放上性能强大且优异的电脑，虚拟现实和载具模拟器设备。我可以在里面待很长时间</span><br><span class="line">I think it must be my playroom. If I had a game room, I wouldn&#x27;t hesitate to put on powerful and excellent computer, virtual reality and vehicle simulator equipment. I can stay in it for a long time</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What makes you feel pleasant in your home?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我在家里的时间不多只有晚上睡觉时才会在家，大部分时间在学校。如果有的话，那一定是放假在家里好好睡个大懒觉和悠闲的生活会在家里感到愉快</span><br><span class="line">I don&#x27;t spend much time at home, only at home when I go to bed at night, and most of the time at school. If anything, it must be a holiday at home, a good night&#x27;s sleep, and a leisurely life will be happy at home</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>What’s the difference between where you are living now and where you have lived in the past?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我过去住的地方房子老一些，人比较少，楼层不高一共6层没有电梯。现在住的地方人很多但是也更吵闹了，楼层很高有32层。周边的饭店也很多</span><br><span class="line">Where I used to live, the house was older, there were fewer people, the floors were not high, there were 6 floors in total, and there was no elevator. Now there are many people living in the place, but it is also more noisy, and the floors are very high, with 32 floors. There are also many restaurants in the surrounding area</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you think it is important to live in a comfortable environment?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">是的，我认为很重要。因为这对生活质量和幸福度的高低有很大的关系。舒适的环境能极大的舒缓人们的压力，使人有更好的心情，减少焦虑，抑郁和很多的心理疾病的产生。并且能够将减少犯罪率。</span><br><span class="line">Yes, I think it&#x27;s important. Because this has a lot to do with quality of life and happiness. A comfortable environment can greatly relieve people&#x27;s stress, make people have a better mood, reduce anxiety, depression and many mental diseases. And will be able to reduce the crime rate.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="Snacks"><a href="#Snacks" class="headerlink" title="Snacks"></a>Snacks</h2><ol><li><p><strong>what snacks do you like to eat?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我喜欢吃的零食是炸鸡、薯片和汽水。这些高热量食物可以使我感到心情愉悦和减轻劳累。</span><br><span class="line">My favorite snacks are fried chicken, chips and soft drinks. These high-calorie foods can make me feel good and less tired.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Did you often eat snacks when you were young?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">虽然我很想吃，但是我并不经常吃。因为父母认为那些是垃圾食品不允许我吃，而且小时候几乎没有零花钱，很难买到。</span><br><span class="line">Although I would love to eat, I don&#x27;t eat it very often. Because my parents thought those were junk foods that I wouldn&#x27;t be allowed to eat, and as a child there was almost no pocket money and it was hard to buy.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>When do you usually eat snacks now?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我现在平时会在晚上吃零食，晚上睡觉前我往往会很馋，而且食欲增长。这时候吃零食也能够减轻一天的疲劳感。想象一下，能够悠闲的坐在电脑或者电视前吃着零食是多么惬意。</span><br><span class="line">I usually snack at night now, and I tend to be hungry at night before going to bed, and my appetite grows. At this time, eating snacks can also reduce the fatigue of the day. Imagine sitting in front of a computer or TV and eating a snack.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you think it is healthy for you to eat snacks?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我不认为吃零食对我是健康的，因为好吃的零食往往是高糖、高盐或者高油脂的，经常吃零食很容易使身体造成很大的负荷，从而引起一系列的慢性疾病。虽然我不认为对我是健康的，但是在快节奏和高压力的大城市下，这是唯一合法的能够以极快速度和低成本的减轻身心劳累、放松和心情愉悦的方法。</span><br><span class="line">I don&#x27;t think snacking is healthy for me, because delicious snacks are often high in sugar, salt or fat, and regular snacking can easily cause a lot of load on the body, resulting in a series of chronic diseases. Although I don&#x27;t think it&#x27;s healthy for me, in a fast-paced and high-stress big city, it&#x27;s the only legal way to reduce physical and mental fatigue, relaxation and happiness at great speed and low cost.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="Weather"><a href="#Weather" class="headerlink" title="Weather"></a>Weather</h2><ol><li><p><strong>what’s the weather like where you live?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">大多数天气比较稳定，变化不会那么大。一般只有夏天像七月和八月会有很多的降雨，季节交替的时候会有较多的风。</span><br><span class="line">Most weather is relatively stable and the changes are not as big. Generally, only in summer, like July and August, there will be a lot of rainfall, and there will be more wind when the seasons change.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you prefer cold or hot weather?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我更喜欢凉的天。因为炎热的天气会使我感到焦躁，而且在凉的天气我就能穿上我喜欢的外套了。</span><br><span class="line">I prefer cool days. Because the hot weather makes me feel agitated, and in the cool weather I can wear my favorite coat.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Do you prefer dry or wet weather?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我更喜欢干燥的天气。因为潮湿的天气我会感到很闷不透气，而且也更容易使食物和衣服发霉</span><br><span class="line">I prefer dry weather. I feel stuffy because of the wet weather, and it&#x27;s also more likely to mold food and clothes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>Are you in the habit of checking the weather forecast? When&#x2F;how often?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">没有这个习惯。我通常只有想起来，或者第二天有特殊事情的时候才会查看天气预报。因为天气预报有时并不准确</span><br><span class="line">There is no such habit. I usually only check the weather forecast when I think about it, or when I have something special the next day. Because weather forecasts are sometimes inaccurate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>what do you think are the effects of climate change in recent years?</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我认为气候变化的影响是越来越频繁的极端天气。由温室效应引起的平均温度升高。导致厄尔尼诺和拉尼娜现象反复交替，极冷和极热将反复出现</span><br><span class="line">I think the impact of climate change is more and more frequent extreme weather. The increase in average temperature caused by the greenhouse effect. This causes El Niño and La Niña to alternate repeatedly, with extreme cold and heat repeatedly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
